Description:
Under Offer
***This property is available for inspection by appointment-Please contact us to arrange a suitable time****
Immaculately maintained this attractive single-level triple fronted brick veneer home provides an environment of instant appeal along with a range of options for those looking to expand, or renew in one of Keilor East's convenient streets. Surrounded by lovely gardens, the home's interior comprises three generous bedrooms plus study, central bathroom, lounge leading through to the dining area and adjoining a timber kitchen with ample pantry storage. Features include polished timber floors, ducted heating and cooling plus an additional beautiful wood fire heater, alarm system and security shutters. Step outside to a wonderful wide undercover entertaining area overlooking the low maintenance backyard complete with an amazing vegie gardens, plus the added appeal of a garage/workshop and carport via gated side driveway. Walking distance to the open spaces of Overland reserve, transport and Milleara Shopping Centre, it's also close to popular primary and secondary schools, as well as easy freeway access. Land approx. 530msq.

We request that you maintain a healthy distance from our team members, and if requested wait outside until the property is ready for the appointment. Lastly, please refrain from touching items/fixtures and doors within the properties. If you would like to view something in particular, please request the agent's assistance. Thank you.

Description:
Leap Into Contemporary Living
Checking off everything on your wish list this sleek and contemporary three bedroom, two bathroom home embodies desirable contemporary living. A bright north-easterly aspect welcomes plentiful light into a private entertainer's courtyard featuring a deck, lawn and colourful roses. Open plan, the spacious interior flows from living and dining areas to a fully equipped kitchen showcasing stone surfaces, a smart island bench and stainless steel appliances including a gas cooktop and dishwasher. All bedrooms offer robes and there's a gleaming family bathroom, plus an ensuite and powder room. Excellent storage, heating, cooling, Holland blinds, an alarm and bamboo flooring add allure and in addition to an automatic garage with direct entry there's an extra parking space on title. A stroll to transport, schools, parkland and walking trails, fantastic for a healthy active lifestyle, this attractive home is also just a short drive to shopping centres and freeway access.

TOWNHOUSE IN A GREAT LOCATION
We have the pleasure to present this lovely Townhouse in a secluded location. It is immaculately presented and offers you comfort and a lifestyle to enjoy. It is located in a sought-after area and is close to all amenities and Schools, Hospital, Train station and Supermarkets in easy reach.
This TOWNHOUSE has 2 good size bedrooms with BIRs, spacious lounge. Formal lounge and open floor Kitchen and dining looking out to a low maintenance courtyard with a pergola.
There is also a very lovely courtyard with decking for outdoor entertaining, split air conditioning upstairs and down, plus ducted heating, lock up garage.
Call now to secure an inspection!

Description:
A Comfortable Family Lifestyle Awaits
INSPECTION STILL AVAILABLE BY APPOINTMENT -
Contact Adrian K - 0475 222 585 or
Anthony Caccamo - 0425 703 312
Superbly appointed throughout with a large and highly flexible floor-plan, offering 4 bedrooms plus study and 4 living zones ideally designed for families that love to entertain.
Upstairs: 4 large bedrooms (all with BIRs) - master with ensuite and WIR, TV area, central bathroom and separate toilet. Downstairs; large study, huge lounge and dining area, family/lounge area, large kitchen, meals area, rumpus/bedroom, family sized laundry and toilet.
Features include ducted heating, 3 split system air conditioners, down-lights, alarm, 3 toilets plus more.
The home is surrounded by sensational low maintenance gardens and set in a quiet but very popular location of Taylors Lakes only minutes away from Overnewton College, Watergardens Shopping Centre & Train Station, local busses, parks and all the best the area has to offer

Description:
Large Family Home
Unlock The Potential In An Exceptional Location
A superb opportunity for savvy home buyers to maximise on the capacity of this wonderful double storey home of 5 bedrooms, 3 Bathrooms which provides a superior setting to enjoy family living. Offering two living areas to effortlessly meet the needs of the largest of families close to all desired amenities!
Ground floor is excellent for extended family or as a separate living zone with a flexible floor plan, including a spacious formal lounge, theatre room, open meals/ family areas with impressive large kitchen with plenty of cupboard space and additional bedroom with bathroom offers convenience and possibilities for elderly parents.
Upstairs reveals an additional 4 carpeted bedrooms with BIRs, served by a centrally located bathroom. A massive master bedroom with en-suite and walk in robe, along with a light filled retreat makes it perfect for families.
Features include ducted heating, air conditioning, high ceilings, Tasmania Oak timber kitchen, dish washer, other features include double garage plus additional extra parking allowing ample room to store a boat, caravan or trailer as well as an alfresco, dining area, ideal for children and pets to enjoy. Ample room to renovate, refurbish to add your personal touches to this substantial family home
All this set on a large corner allotment of 695m2 approx, within a short distance to Keilor Plaza & Water Gardens Shopping Centres, Keilor Downs College, Monmia & St Mary MacKillop Primary Schools, public transport, including Keilor Plains train station, St Albans Leisure Centre, parklands and minutes to Western Ring Road and Calder Freeway. Don't miss out!
Deadline Private Sale closing 5.30pm, 1st may 2020

Description:
listedAS - Lucky Number 8
For a video tour log in to:
https://www.facebook.com/flocarreon.areaspecialist/
Fabulously positioned, this stunning family home promotes a lifestyle of leisure within a friendly community setting. Quality finishes and graceful styling combine to present a warm and welcoming property where that feeling of home radiates from the moment you arrive.
This spectacular home showcases an attractive master bedroom with full ensuite plus walk in robe, also on offer are 2 large bedrooms with built in robes serviced by a gleaming central bathroom with separate toilet. You are then greeted with an elegant kitchen with ample cupboard space and stainless-steel appliances which overlooks an open plan living and dining area.
Other outstanding features include remote-control double garage with drive through access, ducted heating, air conditioning, alarm system, tinted windows, a low maintenance backyard with an added shed for additional storage.
Conveniently situated within walking distance to Cairnlea Shopping Centre, Ginifer train station, bus stop, Victoria University, University Park Primary, Holy Eucharist, Sunshine Hospital, parks, lakes and walking trails.
This is the perfect place to call your own for many years to come.
Our signs are everywhere... winningAS
